<h3><span style="font-family: verdana;"><strong>2. Küre Kapağı</strong></span></h3>
<table border="0" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
    <tbody>
    <tr>
        <td width="100%"><img
                src="images/geometri/Kure/kure6.gif"
